1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] Dok smo slavili, sjetio sam se priče jedne koju smo vi, mislite da ste većina vas čuli, a htio joj vas na tu priču pocijetiti.

2
00:00:08,000 --> 00:00:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] Često mi katolici živimo kao pilići i kokoši, a možemo živjeti kao orlovi.

3
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa tako jedan dan, mali orlič koji se razvio u gnjezdu, odnosno u jajetu, to jaje ispalo iz gnjezda i palo među kokoši i piliće.

4
00:00:32,000 --> 00:00:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] I on se tako razvio među pilićima i kokošima i on je tako zobao, kljucao, jer nije uopće znao da može osvojiti nebeske visine.

5
00:00:45,000 --> 00:00:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] I da može postati ono za što je stvoren.

6
00:00:48,000 --> 00:00:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] I onda ga jedan dan sreo jedan orao i vidio da on zoba tamo s kokošima i pilićima.

7
00:00:56,000 --> 00:01:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] I onda mu je rekao, pa brate šta ti to radiš?

8
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ti zato nisi stvoren.

9
00:01:02,000 --> 00:01:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] I onda ga je polako učio kako da postane ono što je.

10
00:01:08,000 --> 00:01:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tako nekako mi se povezala ta priča s ovom temom koju ću vam danas prezentirati.

11
00:01:15,000 --> 00:01:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] A cijeli dan nekako gledam kao Božju providnost da je vodilo i sve se povezivalo baš prema ovoj temi.

12
00:01:24,000 --> 00:01:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] I ovo slavljanje je, vidjet ćete, jako povezano s onim što ću vam govoriti danas.

13
00:01:30,000 --> 00:01:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] Naime, biskup, sadašnji Robert Baron, tad nije bio biskup, pokrenuo jedan veliki projekt gdje je htio ljudima približiti katolicizam.

14
00:01:44,000 --> 00:01:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] Odnosno, htio je pilićima, tj. orlovima koji su se ponašali kao pilići, pokazati kako mogu letjeti.

15
00:01:54,000 --> 00:02:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] I često mi crkva ovdje ne izvršavamo svoju zadaću da vodimo braću i sestre da postanu ono za što su stvoreni.

16
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da ćemo kroz deset predavanja ove godine, hvala Bogu danas smo uživo, vidjet ćemo moće to ostati tako.

17
00:02:14,000 --> 00:02:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] Blago koje je ovoj knjizi, a on je prošao cijeli svijet zbog ovog projekta, ćemo pokušati i mi nešto uzeti od toga.

18
00:02:26,000 --> 00:02:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa prva tema se zove Zapanjeni i prestrašeni.

19
00:02:31,000 --> 00:02:35,439
[SPEAKER_00] Prije nego što krenem s tom tebom, htio bi nešto kratko o katolicizmu.

20
00:02:35,439 --> 00:02:39,699
[SPEAKER_00] On kaže da je katolicizam najveća ideja koja je ikad postala.

21
00:02:39,699 --> 00:02:49,080
[SPEAKER_00] I da je glavna razlika između katolicizma i ostalih svjetskih religija utjelovljenje, odnosno inkarnacija.

22
00:02:52,000 --> 00:03:03,580
[SPEAKER_00] Recimo neki filozofi, neki učitelji, ne znam, marksisti, sartristi, oni su govorili kako Boga treba izbaciti da bi čovjek postao čovjek do kraja.

23
00:03:05,199 --> 00:03:20,780
[SPEAKER_00] A s tim u suprotnosti je katolicizam koji s tim činom, koji je najveći misterij od svega, koji se dan danas otkriva 2000 godina nakon Isusovog uskrsnuća, nam pokazao istinu o Bogu i o čovjeku.

24
00:03:22,120 --> 00:03:29,060
[SPEAKER_00] Istina je da je Bog postao čovjek i da nije time ugrozio čovjeka, niti ga je uništio.

25
00:03:29,060 --> 00:03:34,580
[SPEAKER_00] Crkveni oci su često ponavljali ovu izreku.

26
00:03:34,580 --> 00:03:39,159
[SPEAKER_00] Bog je postao čovjekom da bi čovjek postao Bogom.

27
00:03:39,159 --> 00:03:43,840
[SPEAKER_00] I u samom tom činu već vidimo najdublji misteri našeg života.

28
00:03:43,840 --> 00:03:48,500
[SPEAKER_00] Najveću moguću ideju koju čovjek ima pred sobom.

29
00:03:48,500 --> 00:03:51,060
[SPEAKER_00] A to je preobrazba u Boga.

30
00:03:52,120 --> 00:03:55,919
[SPEAKER_00] Mi smo stvoreni da bi se jednog dana preobrazili u Boga.

31
00:03:55,919 --> 00:04:02,419
[SPEAKER_00] Nema te ideje, nema te filozofije koja je veća od toga.

32
00:04:02,419 --> 00:04:08,060
[SPEAKER_00] Nema većeg humanizma koji je Isus donio kao revoluciju čovjeku.

33
00:04:08,060 --> 00:04:15,039
[SPEAKER_00] Naš cilj nije neka moralna čistoća, nije ni ekonomsko oslobođenje,

34
00:04:15,039 --> 00:04:22,100
[SPEAKER_00] ni ne znam, umjetničko samoizražavanje, nego je preobrazba u Boga.

35
00:04:22,120 --> 00:04:35,279
[SPEAKER_00] Kažu da je ideja, da je ona jednaka zbroju svih mogućih aspekata i pogleda na tu ideju.

36
00:04:35,279 --> 00:04:42,980
[SPEAKER_00] I zato se ova ideja, kod nas katolika, razvija već 2000 godina.

37
00:04:42,980 --> 00:04:49,699
[SPEAKER_00] I razlika između katolika i drugih hršanskih denominacija je upravo što vide ovu ideju,

38
00:04:49,699 --> 00:04:55,720
[SPEAKER_00] utjelovljenje, kako se razvija kroz prostor i kroz vrijeme.

39
00:04:55,720 --> 00:05:01,519
[SPEAKER_00] A to radi kroz misteri koje je Krist ustanovio, a to je crkva.

40
00:05:02,379 --> 00:05:05,319
[SPEAKER_00] Mi katolici vidimo to utjelovljeme u svemu.

41
00:05:05,319 --> 00:05:10,339
[SPEAKER_00] Vidimo ga u svetohraništu, vidimo ga u kruhu, vidimo ga u vinu.

42
00:05:10,339 --> 00:05:12,699
[SPEAKER_00] Naslučujemo ga u gestama.

43
00:05:12,699 --> 00:05:17,139
[SPEAKER_00] U raspravama teologa.

44
00:05:17,139 --> 00:05:19,879
[SPEAKER_00] U tekstovima koje čitamo.

45
00:05:21,379 --> 00:05:26,180
[SPEAKER_00] Gledamo ga u liturgiji, u pjesmama, u slavljanju Boga.

46
00:05:26,180 --> 00:05:29,980
[SPEAKER_00] I to je razlika.

47
00:05:29,980 --> 00:05:33,980
[SPEAKER_00] Što mi vidimo i imamo puninu te ideje.

48
00:05:33,980 --> 00:05:39,759
[SPEAKER_00] I zato je bitno da shvatimo da je katolicizam

49
00:05:39,759 --> 00:05:47,180
[SPEAKER_00] jednako stvar tijela i osjeta kao i uma i duše.

50
00:05:49,180 --> 00:05:53,800
[SPEAKER_00] Mi katoličku vjeru moramo doživjeti i kroz umjetnost.

51
00:05:53,800 --> 00:05:59,740
[SPEAKER_00] Otac baron, odnosno biskup, često spominje da on vidi

52
00:05:59,740 --> 00:06:02,339
[SPEAKER_00] to utjelovljenje na slučaju ga u katedralama

53
00:06:02,339 --> 00:06:05,199
[SPEAKER_00] koje su gradili katolički arhitekti.

54
00:06:05,199 --> 00:06:07,740
[SPEAKER_00] Da ga vidi i u mozartovim misama.

55
00:06:07,740 --> 00:06:12,500
[SPEAKER_00] Da ga osjeti na raznim mjestima svijeta,

56
00:06:12,500 --> 00:06:14,420
[SPEAKER_00] u svetoj zemlji, u bazilici i groba.

57
00:06:14,420 --> 00:06:18,819
[SPEAKER_00] I to je ono nešto što nama duh sveti daje ovdje

58
00:06:18,819 --> 00:06:19,860
[SPEAKER_00] iskustvo i danas.

59
00:06:19,860 --> 00:06:22,399
[SPEAKER_00] Da ga osjetimo cijelim svojim bićem

60
00:06:22,399 --> 00:06:23,379
[SPEAKER_00] i da ga istražimo.

61
00:06:23,379 --> 00:06:26,240
[SPEAKER_00] I zato ćemo se i mi

62
00:06:26,240 --> 00:06:29,220
[SPEAKER_00] uputiti na to putovanje.

63
00:06:29,220 --> 00:06:31,040
[SPEAKER_00] Kažu da katolička vjera

64
00:06:31,040 --> 00:06:33,819
[SPEAKER_00] je kao crkva koja ima tisuću ulaza.

65
00:06:33,819 --> 00:06:36,040
[SPEAKER_00] I svako može pronaći svoj.

66
00:06:39,040 --> 00:06:44,279
[SPEAKER_00] A Isus je temelj, početak i kraj katoličke vjere.

67
00:06:44,279 --> 00:06:46,120
[SPEAKER_00] I danas ćemo se malo pozabaviti

68
00:06:46,120 --> 00:06:47,759
[SPEAKER_00] gospodinom Isusom.

69
00:06:49,920 --> 00:06:54,879
[SPEAKER_00] Sve je počelo šalom, kaže otac baron.

70
00:06:54,879 --> 00:06:57,220
[SPEAKER_00] Što je šala?

71
00:06:57,220 --> 00:07:02,379
[SPEAKER_00] On kaže šala je kad recimo odrasla osoba glumi bebu.

72
00:07:02,379 --> 00:07:05,699
[SPEAKER_00] Ili beba se ponaša kao odrasla osoba.

73
00:07:05,699 --> 00:07:06,759
[SPEAKER_00] To nas nasmijava.

74
00:07:06,759 --> 00:07:11,259
[SPEAKER_00] Šala bi bila kad vidimo jednog lika kao mister Bina

75
00:07:11,259 --> 00:07:14,920
[SPEAKER_00] da dolazi u ovaj sofisticirani svijet

76
00:07:14,920 --> 00:07:16,160
[SPEAKER_00] i ne zna se ponaša tu.

77
00:07:16,160 --> 00:07:17,939
[SPEAKER_00] To je nama jako smiješno.

78
00:07:17,939 --> 00:07:20,459
[SPEAKER_00] I onda je sve počelo jednom šalom.

79
00:07:20,459 --> 00:07:23,019
[SPEAKER_00] Veliki arhitekt svega,

80
00:07:23,019 --> 00:07:24,480
[SPEAKER_00] tvorac svega, autor,

81
00:07:24,480 --> 00:07:25,899
[SPEAKER_00] postaje čovjek.

82
00:07:25,899 --> 00:07:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nije smiješno, a?

83
00:07:30,000 --> 00:07:40,120
[SPEAKER_00] Da, neki kažu da je srž svakog grijeha

84
00:07:40,120 --> 00:07:42,459
[SPEAKER_00] kad sebe svaćamo preozbiljno.

85
00:07:42,459 --> 00:07:44,120
[SPEAKER_00] I možda nas je baš zato Bog

86
00:07:44,120 --> 00:07:47,579
[SPEAKER_00] pokušao spasiti na šaljiv način.

87
00:07:47,579 --> 00:07:50,279
[SPEAKER_00] Ali,

88
00:07:50,279 --> 00:07:54,139
[SPEAKER_00] ono što je važno je da netko,

89
00:07:54,139 --> 00:07:57,519
[SPEAKER_00] a ne nešto ili riječi ili neki zakon,

90
00:07:57,519 --> 00:08:01,019
[SPEAKER_00] da je to središte naše vjere.

91
00:08:01,019 --> 00:08:02,540
[SPEAKER_00] Nego netko.

92
00:08:02,540 --> 00:08:04,779
[SPEAKER_00] Osoba Isusa Hrista.

93
00:08:04,779 --> 00:08:07,459
[SPEAKER_00] Pa tko je taj čovjek?

94
00:08:07,459 --> 00:08:10,079
[SPEAKER_00] On je bio židov.

95
00:08:11,040 --> 00:08:12,560
[SPEAKER_00] Malo toga znamo o njemu

96
00:08:12,560 --> 00:08:14,879
[SPEAKER_00] za njegovih ranih godina.

97
00:08:14,879 --> 00:08:16,879
[SPEAKER_00] Znamo samo da se izgubio u hramu.

98
00:08:16,879 --> 00:08:19,120
[SPEAKER_00] Da su ga sretno pronašli.

99
00:08:20,339 --> 00:08:21,680
[SPEAKER_00] znamo da je bio drvodjeljen sin.

100
00:08:21,680 --> 00:08:25,800
[SPEAKER_00] Ono što još znamo da nije bio neki učitelj religiozni,

101
00:08:25,800 --> 00:08:31,800
[SPEAKER_00] da nije pripadao nijednoj tadašnjoj ni farizejima, ni saducejima, ni jesenima.

102
00:08:32,679 --> 00:08:34,860
[SPEAKER_00] Znači našim rječnikom on je bio lajk.

103
00:08:34,860 --> 00:08:40,639
[SPEAKER_00] Ali isto tako znamo da je s 30 godina počeo javno djelovati.

104
00:08:40,639 --> 00:08:44,879
[SPEAKER_00] I onda je došao sa autoritetom bez presedana.

105
00:08:44,879 --> 00:08:48,779
[SPEAKER_00] Taj lajk došao bi među židove i rekao,

106
00:08:48,779 --> 00:08:52,200
[SPEAKER_00] čuli ste da je pisano,

107
00:08:53,000 --> 00:08:54,740
[SPEAKER_00] a ja vam kažem.

108
00:08:54,740 --> 00:08:57,779
[SPEAKER_00] Znači on govori o tori.

109
00:08:57,779 --> 00:09:00,399
[SPEAKER_00] Moramo učiti da je židovski mentalitet.

110
00:09:00,399 --> 00:09:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] On govori o zakonima koje je dao Mojsije.

111
00:09:04,000 --> 00:09:07,379
[SPEAKER_00] To je bio ko danas kanon i katekizam.

112
00:09:07,379 --> 00:09:09,879
[SPEAKER_00] On kaže čuli ste da je pisano,

113
00:09:09,879 --> 00:09:11,559
[SPEAKER_00] a ja vam kažem.

114
00:09:11,559 --> 00:09:17,419
[SPEAKER_00] I to je ljude zaprepastilo.

115
00:09:17,419 --> 00:09:21,179
[SPEAKER_00] U isto vrijeme dolazi jednom čovjeku

116
00:09:21,179 --> 00:09:24,139
[SPEAKER_00] koji je paraliziran odrasli moškarac

117
00:09:24,139 --> 00:09:27,360
[SPEAKER_00] kaže, sinko, otpuštaj ti se tvoji grijesi.

118
00:09:27,360 --> 00:09:29,360
[SPEAKER_00] Oni su rekli pa ovaj huli.

119
00:09:29,360 --> 00:09:32,899
[SPEAKER_00] Ko može oprastati grijehe ako ne samo Bog?

120
00:09:32,899 --> 00:09:36,240
[SPEAKER_00] U isto vrijeme je taj Isus

121
00:09:36,240 --> 00:09:38,440
[SPEAKER_00] smirio je o luju.

122
00:09:38,440 --> 00:09:41,639
[SPEAKER_00] Vidimo ima moć nad prirodom.

123
00:09:41,639 --> 00:09:48,519
[SPEAKER_00] I privlači svu pažnju na sebe.

124
00:09:50,360 --> 00:09:55,259
[SPEAKER_00] I o njemu je pisano da su svi bili zaprepašteni

125
00:09:55,259 --> 00:09:57,820
[SPEAKER_00] i da je glas o njemu

126
00:09:57,820 --> 00:10:01,580
[SPEAKER_00] da je glas o njemu pukao po svom kraju gdje je išao.

127
00:10:01,580 --> 00:10:06,399
[SPEAKER_00] I silne gomile i mnoštvo su dolazile ga slušati.

128
00:10:06,399 --> 00:10:09,860
[SPEAKER_00] I sad neki su dolazili vjerojatno da se osvjedoče

129
00:10:09,860 --> 00:10:12,500
[SPEAKER_00] da on činio čudesa.

130
00:10:13,240 --> 00:10:16,419
[SPEAKER_00] Neki su došli slušati tog karizmatičnog propovjednika,

131
00:10:16,419 --> 00:10:18,139
[SPEAKER_00] čuti njegove riječi,

132
00:10:18,139 --> 00:10:20,399
[SPEAKER_00] želi su čuti nešto pametno.

133
00:10:20,399 --> 00:10:22,620
[SPEAKER_00] Neki su dolazili,

134
00:10:22,620 --> 00:10:25,059
[SPEAKER_00] znam takve sigurno ih imao ovdje,

135
00:10:25,059 --> 00:10:26,720
[SPEAKER_00] što je bilo slavna osoba

136
00:10:26,720 --> 00:10:27,980
[SPEAKER_00] i bilo je lijepo biti vidjen

137
00:10:27,980 --> 00:10:29,500
[SPEAKER_00] pored slavne osobe.

138
00:10:30,340 --> 00:10:32,259
[SPEAKER_00] Kad smo mlađi pa imamo malo do Isusa,

139
00:10:32,259 --> 00:10:33,799
[SPEAKER_00] ajmo, možda nas neko vidi tamo.

140
00:10:33,799 --> 00:10:37,779
[SPEAKER_00] Ali svi su se na koncu oni pitali

141
00:10:37,779 --> 00:10:39,419
[SPEAKER_00] tko je taj čovjek.

142
00:10:39,419 --> 00:10:43,559
[SPEAKER_00] I to je pitanje bitno i danas,

143
00:10:43,559 --> 00:10:45,039
[SPEAKER_00] za svakog od nas.

144
00:10:45,039 --> 00:10:46,659
[SPEAKER_00] Tko je taj čovjek?

145
00:10:46,659 --> 00:10:54,100
[SPEAKER_00] Negdje na polovici svog apostolskog djelovanja,

146
00:10:54,100 --> 00:10:55,759
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno svoje javne službe,

147
00:10:55,759 --> 00:10:59,559
[SPEAKER_00] Isus je bio na sjeveru obećanje zemlje,

148
00:10:59,620 --> 00:11:00,860
[SPEAKER_00] u Cezarei Filipovoj.

149
00:11:00,860 --> 00:11:04,960
[SPEAKER_00] I tamo je pitao učenik jedno pitanje.

150
00:11:04,960 --> 00:11:06,240
[SPEAKER_00] Pitao ih je,

151
00:11:06,240 --> 00:11:09,360
[SPEAKER_00] što ljudi kažu tko sam ja?

152
00:11:09,360 --> 00:11:12,820
[SPEAKER_00] I ovako puno puta smo čuli za tu rečenicu,

153
00:11:12,820 --> 00:11:15,100
[SPEAKER_00] onako, pa dobro, zanimalo ga.

154
00:11:15,100 --> 00:11:17,620
[SPEAKER_00] Ali to je zapravo jako čudna rečenica.

155
00:11:17,620 --> 00:11:20,799
[SPEAKER_00] Bilo bi možda bolje da je,

156
00:11:20,799 --> 00:11:23,139
[SPEAKER_00] ono, bilo bi nam lakše shvatiti da je pito

157
00:11:23,139 --> 00:11:24,759
[SPEAKER_00] što ljudi misle o meni,

158
00:11:24,759 --> 00:11:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] što ljudi misle o onom što sam ja napravio neki dan,

159
00:11:27,000 --> 00:11:28,220
[SPEAKER_00] za ono što sam rekao,

160
00:11:28,220 --> 00:11:29,200
[SPEAKER_00] ali se neko naljutio.

161
00:11:29,379 --> 00:11:31,399
[SPEAKER_00] To su normalnija pitanja.

162
00:11:31,399 --> 00:11:35,059
[SPEAKER_00] Ali on pita što ljudi kažu tko sam ja.

163
00:11:36,720 --> 00:11:39,159
[SPEAKER_00] To je pitanje o njegovom identitetu.

164
00:11:39,159 --> 00:11:43,919
[SPEAKER_00] Veliki osnivači religija, recimo Buda,

165
00:11:43,919 --> 00:11:47,600
[SPEAKER_00] on je nikad nije privlačio pozornost na sebe.

166
00:11:47,600 --> 00:11:49,720
[SPEAKER_00] On je čak zazirao od toga.

167
00:11:49,720 --> 00:11:52,539
[SPEAKER_00] On je ljude upučivao u duhovnost,

168
00:11:52,539 --> 00:11:54,700
[SPEAKER_00] da idu duhovnim putem i da će ih to osloboditi.

169
00:11:56,360 --> 00:12:00,460
[SPEAKER_00] Jan Mohamed, on je čovjek koji je za sebe rekao da je dobio

170
00:12:00,460 --> 00:12:04,360
[SPEAKER_00] konačnu objavu Alaha, Boga.

171
00:12:04,360 --> 00:12:07,860
[SPEAKER_00] I opet nije toliko privlačio pažnju na sebe,

172
00:12:07,860 --> 00:12:10,360
[SPEAKER_00] nego mu je više bilo stavilo da svi čitaju taj Kuran

173
00:12:10,360 --> 00:12:11,600
[SPEAKER_00] i da slijede pravila.

174
00:12:12,299 --> 00:12:14,440
[SPEAKER_00] Confucije, ne znam ko je čuo za njega.

175
00:12:14,440 --> 00:12:19,559
[SPEAKER_00] Ali on je bio neki etički učitelj

176
00:12:19,559 --> 00:12:22,679
[SPEAKER_00] koji je došao na nekom pronicavošću

177
00:12:22,679 --> 00:12:23,960
[SPEAKER_00] do nekih pravila života

178
00:12:23,960 --> 00:12:28,480
[SPEAKER_00] koje bi ljudima donio neki skladan život.

179
00:12:28,480 --> 00:12:31,120
[SPEAKER_00] Ali opet nije privlačio pažnju na sebe.

180
00:12:31,120 --> 00:12:35,740
[SPEAKER_00] Kako je govorio za ratrustra i tako dalje.

181
00:12:35,740 --> 00:12:38,240
[SPEAKER_00] Onda dođe Isus.

182
00:12:41,240 --> 00:12:43,120
[SPEAKER_00] I moramo odgovoriti na to pitanje.

183
00:12:43,120 --> 00:12:44,899
[SPEAKER_00] Ono je jako bitno.

184
00:12:44,899 --> 00:12:46,519
[SPEAKER_00] I postoje tri solucije.

185
00:12:46,519 --> 00:12:50,019
[SPEAKER_00] Postoji da je stvarno bio Bog,

186
00:12:50,019 --> 00:12:52,240
[SPEAKER_00] kako je govorio za sebe.

187
00:12:52,240 --> 00:12:57,799
[SPEAKER_00] Postoji solucija da je bio luđak,

188
00:12:57,799 --> 00:12:59,779
[SPEAKER_00] što isto moguće mislim.

189
00:12:59,779 --> 00:13:03,259
[SPEAKER_00] Bilo je luđaka uvijek i u umobolnice sad kad odete

190
00:13:03,259 --> 00:13:05,799
[SPEAKER_00] sigurno će neko za sebe reći da je Bog.

191
00:13:05,799 --> 00:13:08,679
[SPEAKER_00] I zbog toga su ga čak na kraju i ubili.

192
00:13:10,179 --> 00:13:14,200
[SPEAKER_00] Vidjeli su i rekli su da on za sebe govori

193
00:13:14,200 --> 00:13:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] da je sin Boga oca i da se uspoređuje.

194
00:13:18,000 --> 00:13:20,039
[SPEAKER_00] Zbog toga su ga farizei ubili.

195
00:13:20,039 --> 00:13:23,440
[SPEAKER_00] Ili postoje neko srednje rješenje.

196
00:13:23,440 --> 00:13:25,720
[SPEAKER_00] Da je bio neki filozof.

197
00:13:25,720 --> 00:13:26,740
[SPEAKER_00] I to sad nastane.

198
00:13:26,740 --> 00:13:29,600
[SPEAKER_00] Da je bio neki moralni učitelj.

199
00:13:29,600 --> 00:13:32,960
[SPEAKER_00] Da je bio veliki nadahnuti religiozni prosvjetitelj.

200
00:13:32,960 --> 00:13:37,139
[SPEAKER_00] I takve teorije su nastale sad nedavno vjerojatno u naslonjačima.

201
00:13:38,799 --> 00:13:41,480
[SPEAKER_00] Ali kogod malo bolje čita evanđelje,

202
00:13:41,480 --> 00:13:46,220
[SPEAKER_00] vidi i brzo svača da to ne može biti tako.

203
00:13:47,740 --> 00:13:51,700
[SPEAKER_00] Ili je Bog, kao što je govorio za sebe,

204
00:13:51,700 --> 00:13:54,360
[SPEAKER_00] ili je loš čovjek ili laže.

205
00:13:54,360 --> 00:14:04,500
[SPEAKER_00] Ide toliko daleko taj Isus da poziva na izbor.

206
00:14:04,500 --> 00:14:06,080
[SPEAKER_00] O tome smo čuli kroz molitu.

207
00:14:06,759 --> 00:14:08,840
[SPEAKER_00] I današnje evanđelje nam to kaže.

208
00:14:08,840 --> 00:14:11,940
[SPEAKER_00] On kaže, tko nije sa mnom protiv mene?

209
00:14:11,940 --> 00:14:16,299
[SPEAKER_00] Tko sa mnom ne sabire taj rasipa?

210
00:14:16,299 --> 00:14:20,519
[SPEAKER_00] I možda je to malo za današnje društvo,

211
00:14:20,519 --> 00:14:23,940
[SPEAKER_00] za naše osjetljivo društvo preoštro.

212
00:14:23,940 --> 00:14:28,460
[SPEAKER_00] Ali kad odgovorimo na to pitanje,

213
00:14:28,460 --> 00:14:31,679
[SPEAKER_00] i na kraju svega naša kršćanska evangelizacija

214
00:14:31,679 --> 00:14:33,220
[SPEAKER_00] se svodi na taj izbor.

215
00:14:33,220 --> 00:14:35,019
[SPEAKER_00] Ili jesi ili nisi?

216
00:14:36,500 --> 00:14:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jesi s njim ili protiv njega?

217
00:14:38,000 --> 00:14:45,659
[SPEAKER_00] A njegovo božanstvo kako izgleda?

218
00:14:45,659 --> 00:14:46,840
[SPEAKER_00] Ivan Krstitelj kad je,

219
00:14:46,840 --> 00:14:50,419
[SPEAKER_00] kad je dva učenika su ga pitali,

220
00:14:50,419 --> 00:14:53,220
[SPEAKER_00] on je poslao dva učenika da slijede Isusa.

221
00:14:53,220 --> 00:14:56,759
[SPEAKER_00] I oni su došli Isusu i pitali ga,

222
00:14:56,759 --> 00:14:59,139
[SPEAKER_00] gdje ja stanuješ učitelju?

223
00:14:59,139 --> 00:15:03,120
[SPEAKER_00] I on kaže, dođite sa mnom i vidite.

224
00:15:03,120 --> 00:15:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] Isto čuli puno puta,

225
00:15:06,240 --> 00:15:07,659
[SPEAKER_00] ali to je revolucija.

226
00:15:07,659 --> 00:15:13,200
[SPEAKER_00] Ovdje on pokazuje da je bitnije za kršćansko učeništvo,

227
00:15:13,200 --> 00:15:14,620
[SPEAKER_00] Isusovo učeništvo,

228
00:15:14,620 --> 00:15:15,940
[SPEAKER_00] boraviti s njim,

229
00:15:15,940 --> 00:15:17,580
[SPEAKER_00] možda nego

230
00:15:17,580 --> 00:15:20,179
[SPEAKER_00] njegova riječ.

231
00:15:20,179 --> 00:15:22,519
[SPEAKER_00] Daleko od toga da je bitna,

232
00:15:22,519 --> 00:15:24,840
[SPEAKER_00] posebno kad znamo i vjerujemo da je Bog.

233
00:15:25,679 --> 00:15:29,340
[SPEAKER_00] ali biti s njim je revolucija.

234
00:15:30,019 --> 00:15:32,059
[SPEAKER_00] zašto je on privlačio pažnju na sebe?

235
00:15:32,059 --> 00:15:35,279
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto su svi toliko bili okupirani njime?

236
00:15:36,980 --> 00:15:39,100
[SPEAKER_00] pa baš zato što je govorio kao Bog.

237
00:15:41,899 --> 00:15:42,899
[SPEAKER_00] On je rekao,

238
00:15:42,899 --> 00:15:45,200
[SPEAKER_00] nebo će iz zemlja proć

239
00:15:45,200 --> 00:15:46,740
[SPEAKER_00] i u minuti,

240
00:15:46,740 --> 00:15:49,039
[SPEAKER_00] a moje riječi ne, neće nikada.

241
00:15:49,039 --> 00:15:50,840
[SPEAKER_00] To nije rekao niko,

242
00:15:50,840 --> 00:15:51,740
[SPEAKER_00] nijedan filozof.

243
00:15:52,779 --> 00:15:54,019
[SPEAKER_00] Svi se boje tak nešto reći,

244
00:15:54,019 --> 00:15:55,940
[SPEAKER_00] ali znaju koliko su riječi prolazne.

245
00:15:55,940 --> 00:15:57,320
[SPEAKER_00] On kaže,

246
00:15:57,320 --> 00:15:58,940
[SPEAKER_00] moje riječi neće nikad proći.

247
00:15:58,940 --> 00:16:01,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ili još dalje.

248
00:16:01,539 --> 00:16:02,440
[SPEAKER_00] On kaže,

249
00:16:02,440 --> 00:16:05,519
[SPEAKER_00] tko mene ne ljubi,

250
00:16:05,519 --> 00:16:06,980
[SPEAKER_00] to jest,

251
00:16:06,980 --> 00:16:08,539
[SPEAKER_00] tko ljubi više oca i majku

252
00:16:08,539 --> 00:16:09,220
[SPEAKER_00] nego mene,

253
00:16:09,220 --> 00:16:10,679
[SPEAKER_00] nije me dostojan.

254
00:16:10,679 --> 00:16:12,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ko bi to rekao?

255
00:16:12,960 --> 00:16:14,659
[SPEAKER_00] Koji religijski vođa?

256
00:16:14,659 --> 00:16:16,460
[SPEAKER_00] A je dobro da kaže,

257
00:16:16,460 --> 00:16:18,299
[SPEAKER_00] moraš ljubiti Boga više od svog života

258
00:16:18,299 --> 00:16:20,100
[SPEAKER_00] ili moraš ljubiti moje riječi,

259
00:16:20,100 --> 00:16:21,320
[SPEAKER_00] ono što sam dobio od Boga.

260
00:16:22,220 --> 00:16:23,059
[SPEAKER_00] Ako je rekao mene,

261
00:16:23,059 --> 00:16:25,159
[SPEAKER_00] moraš mene ljubiti.

262
00:16:25,159 --> 00:16:29,039
[SPEAKER_00] Isus sebe stavlja u centar.

263
00:16:29,039 --> 00:16:33,820
[SPEAKER_00] I jedan od dokaza da Isus bio Bog

264
00:16:33,820 --> 00:16:40,460
[SPEAKER_00] donosi nam jedna kratka rečenica

265
00:16:40,460 --> 00:16:42,279
[SPEAKER_00] u Markovom evanđelju

266
00:16:42,279 --> 00:16:44,539
[SPEAKER_00] kad je Isus putovao u Jeruzalem.

267
00:16:44,539 --> 00:16:46,639
[SPEAKER_00] On kaže ovako,

268
00:16:46,639 --> 00:16:49,659
[SPEAKER_00] putovali su tako uzlazeći u Jeruzalem

269
00:16:49,659 --> 00:16:51,879
[SPEAKER_00] govorići za Isusa i njegove učenike.

270
00:16:51,879 --> 00:16:55,059
[SPEAKER_00] Isus je išao pred njima

271
00:16:55,059 --> 00:16:57,299
[SPEAKER_00] te bijahu zaprepašteni,

272
00:16:57,299 --> 00:16:59,620
[SPEAKER_00] a oni koji su išli za njim

273
00:16:59,620 --> 00:17:00,779
[SPEAKER_00] prestrašeni.

274
00:17:00,779 --> 00:17:04,140
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto bi neko koji se toliko družio

275
00:17:04,140 --> 00:17:06,700
[SPEAKER_00] s Isusom bio prestrašen i zapanjen?

276
00:17:11,200 --> 00:17:15,819
[SPEAKER_00] Oni su u njemu doživjeli su dva osjećaja,

277
00:17:15,819 --> 00:17:17,440
[SPEAKER_00] strah i strah opoštovanje.

278
00:17:17,440 --> 00:17:22,180
[SPEAKER_00] A to su vam jedina dva osjećaja koja se u starom zavetu bude

279
00:17:22,180 --> 00:17:24,779
[SPEAKER_00] kao reakcija na Boga.

280
00:17:24,779 --> 00:17:27,339
[SPEAKER_00] Strah i strah opoštovanje.

281
00:17:27,339 --> 00:17:35,880
[SPEAKER_00] Što je taj Isus, da vam još malo dokažem,

282
00:17:35,880 --> 00:17:37,400
[SPEAKER_00] treba učiniti.

283
00:17:39,039 --> 00:17:41,480
[SPEAKER_00] Za židove Jahve

284
00:17:41,480 --> 00:17:44,740
[SPEAKER_00] je trebao učiniti, odnosno Mesija,

285
00:17:44,740 --> 00:17:45,500
[SPEAKER_00] četiri stvari.

286
00:17:45,500 --> 00:17:47,119
[SPEAKER_00] On je trebao

287
00:17:47,119 --> 00:17:49,160
[SPEAKER_00] sabrati izraelska plemena,

288
00:17:49,160 --> 00:17:52,079
[SPEAKER_00] očistiti jeruzalemski hram,

289
00:17:52,079 --> 00:17:53,960
[SPEAKER_00] izaći na kraj

290
00:17:53,960 --> 00:17:55,819
[SPEAKER_00] sa neprijateljima naroda

291
00:17:55,819 --> 00:17:59,279
[SPEAKER_00] i vladat kao gospodin neba i zemlje.

292
00:17:59,279 --> 00:18:02,380
[SPEAKER_00] I na taj način će se Izrael pročistiti

293
00:18:02,380 --> 00:18:04,079
[SPEAKER_00] i na taj način će

294
00:18:04,079 --> 00:18:07,539
[SPEAKER_00] donijeti spasenje svijetu.

295
00:18:07,539 --> 00:18:12,259
[SPEAKER_00] I prvi kršćani su vidjeli

296
00:18:12,259 --> 00:18:15,279
[SPEAKER_00] da je Isus sve te četiri stvari ispunio,

297
00:18:15,279 --> 00:18:17,599
[SPEAKER_00] ali na potpuno neočekivan način.

298
00:18:17,599 --> 00:18:19,259
[SPEAKER_00] Pa ajmo jednu po jednu.

299
00:18:19,259 --> 00:18:24,079
[SPEAKER_00] Kad kažem da je trebao sabrati izraelska plemena,

300
00:18:25,819 --> 00:18:28,579
[SPEAKER_00] ajmo ući u kontekst židovstva

301
00:18:28,579 --> 00:18:29,619
[SPEAKER_00] i ući u tu priču.

302
00:18:29,619 --> 00:18:33,980
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, Bog kad je vidio

303
00:18:33,980 --> 00:18:37,339
[SPEAKER_00] veliku zloču čovjeka,

304
00:18:37,339 --> 00:18:38,980
[SPEAKER_00] kako ga je napustio,

305
00:18:38,980 --> 00:18:41,420
[SPEAKER_00] on je odredio plan spasenja.

306
00:18:41,420 --> 00:18:43,140
[SPEAKER_00] I on je izgledao nekako ovako.

307
00:18:43,140 --> 00:18:45,880
[SPEAKER_00] Odabrao Abrahama i njegovo potomstvo

308
00:18:45,880 --> 00:18:47,660
[SPEAKER_00] da mu budu narod vjeran.

309
00:18:47,660 --> 00:18:50,440
[SPEAKER_00] Posebno ih je ljubio

310
00:18:50,440 --> 00:18:52,960
[SPEAKER_00] i dao im je svečeničku službu.

311
00:18:54,039 --> 00:18:56,140
[SPEAKER_00] da preko te svečeničke službe

312
00:18:56,140 --> 00:18:57,119
[SPEAKER_00] žive čestito

313
00:18:57,119 --> 00:18:59,180
[SPEAKER_00] i da budu magnet za druge narode.

314
00:18:59,180 --> 00:19:04,619
[SPEAKER_00] Pa onda imamo to kroz proroke,

315
00:19:04,619 --> 00:19:06,400
[SPEAKER_00] kroz vidimo tu čežnju

316
00:19:06,400 --> 00:19:08,140
[SPEAKER_00] u Izaiji da Sion

317
00:19:08,140 --> 00:19:09,700
[SPEAKER_00] bude gora nad svim gorama.

318
00:19:09,700 --> 00:19:13,660
[SPEAKER_00] Da svi narodi dolaze na taj Sion

319
00:19:13,660 --> 00:19:14,680
[SPEAKER_00] i klanjaju se Bogu.

320
00:19:16,680 --> 00:19:18,859
[SPEAKER_00] Ali često kroz povijest

321
00:19:18,859 --> 00:19:20,880
[SPEAKER_00] izraelskog naroda

322
00:19:20,880 --> 00:19:22,180
[SPEAKER_00] oni su otpali.

323
00:19:22,180 --> 00:19:25,400
[SPEAKER_00] Počeli se klanjati drugim bogovima,

324
00:19:25,400 --> 00:19:28,039
[SPEAKER_00] krivo bogoštovlje,

325
00:19:28,039 --> 00:19:31,180
[SPEAKER_00] počeli su štovat bogove

326
00:19:31,180 --> 00:19:33,140
[SPEAKER_00] koji su okolni narodi štovali.

327
00:19:33,140 --> 00:19:35,559
[SPEAKER_00] Često bili nacionalisti,

328
00:19:35,559 --> 00:19:38,799
[SPEAKER_00] odali se hedonizmu, novcu.

329
00:19:42,799 --> 00:19:44,680
[SPEAKER_00] i tako bili raspršeni.

330
00:19:44,680 --> 00:19:47,259
[SPEAKER_00] Jer bi došli okolni narodi

331
00:19:47,259 --> 00:19:49,400
[SPEAKER_00] i oni ne bi bili ujedinjeni

332
00:19:49,400 --> 00:19:52,859
[SPEAKER_00] i često bi ih odveli u progonstvo,

333
00:19:52,859 --> 00:19:54,039
[SPEAKER_00] Asirci, Babilonci,

334
00:19:54,039 --> 00:19:56,299
[SPEAKER_00] prije toga Egipćani.

335
00:19:56,299 --> 00:19:58,539
[SPEAKER_00] I kažu za Džavla

336
00:19:58,539 --> 00:19:59,079
[SPEAKER_00] da je on,

337
00:19:59,079 --> 00:20:01,500
[SPEAKER_00] jedan od prvih naziva

338
00:20:01,500 --> 00:20:02,579
[SPEAKER_00] biblijskih za njega je

339
00:20:02,579 --> 00:20:03,779
[SPEAKER_00] Diablos.

340
00:20:05,779 --> 00:20:07,500
[SPEAKER_00] Diabelion je jedna izvedenica

341
00:20:07,500 --> 00:20:09,079
[SPEAKER_00] koja znači razdijelitelj,

342
00:20:09,079 --> 00:20:11,079
[SPEAKER_00] raspršitelj.

343
00:20:11,079 --> 00:20:15,039
[SPEAKER_00] Ako je bog snaga koja skuplja,

344
00:20:15,039 --> 00:20:17,539
[SPEAKER_00] ovo što smo čuli danas na molitvi,

345
00:20:17,539 --> 00:20:19,079
[SPEAKER_00] bog nas je skupio,

346
00:20:19,079 --> 00:20:20,519
[SPEAKER_00] bog skuplja,

347
00:20:20,519 --> 00:20:25,880
[SPEAKER_00] grijeh je snaga koja nas razdvaja.

348
00:20:29,420 --> 00:20:30,140
[SPEAKER_00] I zato je

349
00:20:30,140 --> 00:20:32,079
[SPEAKER_00] čežnja izraelskog naroda

350
00:20:32,079 --> 00:20:33,539
[SPEAKER_00] bila da se ponovno skupe.

351
00:20:33,539 --> 00:20:38,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ezekijel je

352
00:20:38,380 --> 00:20:40,500
[SPEAKER_00] govorio o izraelskom narodu

353
00:20:40,500 --> 00:20:41,400
[SPEAKER_00] kao o ovcama

354
00:20:41,400 --> 00:20:42,940
[SPEAKER_00] koji su razbacane po brdu.

355
00:20:42,940 --> 00:20:44,980
[SPEAKER_00] I pazite,

356
00:20:44,980 --> 00:20:46,779
[SPEAKER_00] Isus zna u kojem kontekstu on živi.

357
00:20:46,779 --> 00:20:48,519
[SPEAKER_00] I on dođe i kaže

358
00:20:48,519 --> 00:20:49,940
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam pastir dobri.

359
00:20:49,940 --> 00:20:53,940
[SPEAKER_00] On je taj koji treba

360
00:20:53,940 --> 00:20:55,680
[SPEAKER_00] skupiti ovce Izraelove.

361
00:20:57,319 --> 00:20:58,720
[SPEAKER_00] Kad je počeo propovijeda,

362
00:20:58,720 --> 00:20:59,680
[SPEAKER_00] došao i rekao je

363
00:20:59,680 --> 00:21:02,299
[SPEAKER_00] približilo se kraljestvo Božje.

364
00:21:02,299 --> 00:21:04,960
[SPEAKER_00] Obratite se i vjerujte evanđelju.

365
00:21:04,960 --> 00:21:06,099
[SPEAKER_00] Na prvi pogled onako,

366
00:21:06,099 --> 00:21:07,099
[SPEAKER_00] dosta duhovno,

367
00:21:07,099 --> 00:21:08,720
[SPEAKER_00] kraljestvo Božje,

368
00:21:08,720 --> 00:21:10,779
[SPEAKER_00] ono, pisalo se 2000 godina

369
00:21:10,779 --> 00:21:12,039
[SPEAKER_00] je se već potrošilo tinte

370
00:21:12,039 --> 00:21:14,640
[SPEAKER_00] da se opiše šta je kraljestvo Božje.

371
00:21:14,640 --> 00:21:16,119
[SPEAKER_00] Ali jedan teolog kaže

372
00:21:16,119 --> 00:21:17,759
[SPEAKER_00] da su prvi židove u tome čuli

373
00:21:17,759 --> 00:21:20,220
[SPEAKER_00] sabiru se plemena.

374
00:21:20,220 --> 00:21:22,680
[SPEAKER_00] Oni su dobro znali šta to znači.

375
00:21:22,680 --> 00:21:24,579
[SPEAKER_00] Sabiru se plemena.

376
00:21:24,579 --> 00:21:26,839
[SPEAKER_00] Isus je krenuo

377
00:21:26,839 --> 00:21:27,960
[SPEAKER_00] sabirat plemena.

378
00:21:27,960 --> 00:21:29,460
[SPEAKER_00] I kako je on to činio?

379
00:21:29,460 --> 00:21:31,460
[SPEAKER_00] Ne na onaj način

380
00:21:31,460 --> 00:21:32,599
[SPEAKER_00] koji su oni očekivali.

381
00:21:32,599 --> 00:21:34,980
[SPEAKER_00] Isus je koristio

382
00:21:34,980 --> 00:21:36,440
[SPEAKER_00] principe inkluzivnosti

383
00:21:36,440 --> 00:21:37,039
[SPEAKER_00] koji su danas

384
00:21:37,039 --> 00:21:37,980
[SPEAKER_00] toliko poželjni.

385
00:21:37,980 --> 00:21:39,539
[SPEAKER_00] Imao je taj princip

386
00:21:39,539 --> 00:21:40,640
[SPEAKER_00] okruglog stola.

387
00:21:40,640 --> 00:21:43,619
[SPEAKER_00] Svi su mogli doći.

388
00:21:43,619 --> 00:21:44,420
[SPEAKER_00] Carinici,

389
00:21:44,420 --> 00:21:45,740
[SPEAKER_00] bludnici,

390
00:21:45,740 --> 00:21:47,000
[SPEAKER_00] hromi,

391
00:21:47,000 --> 00:21:47,680
[SPEAKER_00] bolesni.

392
00:21:51,180 --> 00:21:52,259
[SPEAKER_00] on je počeo

393
00:21:52,259 --> 00:21:53,200
[SPEAKER_00] sabirat one

394
00:21:53,200 --> 00:21:55,039
[SPEAKER_00] one slojeve društva

395
00:21:55,039 --> 00:21:56,299
[SPEAKER_00] gdje je podjela društvena

396
00:21:56,299 --> 00:21:57,519
[SPEAKER_00] bila najizraženija.

397
00:21:57,519 --> 00:22:00,259
[SPEAKER_00] I to je radosna vijez za nas.

398
00:22:00,259 --> 00:22:02,279
[SPEAKER_00] Odbačene,

399
00:22:02,279 --> 00:22:03,420
[SPEAKER_00] bolesne.

400
00:22:03,420 --> 00:22:04,579
[SPEAKER_00] Baš zato je ozdravio

401
00:22:04,579 --> 00:22:05,799
[SPEAKER_00] toliko puno bolesnih.

402
00:22:05,799 --> 00:22:07,299
[SPEAKER_00] Zato što se bolest

403
00:22:07,299 --> 00:22:08,960
[SPEAKER_00] tad smatrala kao kaznom za grijehe.

404
00:22:09,799 --> 00:22:10,859
[SPEAKER_00] I koje bolest

405
00:22:10,859 --> 00:22:11,819
[SPEAKER_00] a nije mogo potpuno

406
00:22:11,819 --> 00:22:14,039
[SPEAKER_00] ostvariti svoj potpuni život

407
00:22:14,039 --> 00:22:14,859
[SPEAKER_00] u zajednici.

408
00:22:14,859 --> 00:22:18,640
[SPEAKER_00] On liječi.

409
00:22:18,640 --> 00:22:21,559
[SPEAKER_00] I neumoljiv je oko toga.

410
00:22:21,559 --> 00:22:23,160
[SPEAKER_00] Ruši sve norme

411
00:22:23,160 --> 00:22:24,220
[SPEAKER_00] koje mu stavljaju na put

412
00:22:24,220 --> 00:22:26,400
[SPEAKER_00] i stavlja kraljevstvo Božje

413
00:22:26,400 --> 00:22:27,160
[SPEAKER_00] na prvo mjesto.

414
00:22:27,160 --> 00:22:31,039
[SPEAKER_00] Ruši norme farizejske.

415
00:22:31,039 --> 00:22:33,880
[SPEAKER_00] Subot ukrši.

416
00:22:33,880 --> 00:22:34,839
[SPEAKER_00] Samo radi toga.

417
00:22:34,839 --> 00:22:35,559
[SPEAKER_00] Radi čovjeka

418
00:22:35,559 --> 00:22:36,619
[SPEAKER_00] da ga dovuče sebi.

419
00:22:36,619 --> 00:22:39,500
[SPEAKER_00] Uključuje

420
00:22:39,500 --> 00:22:40,640
[SPEAKER_00] svoj narod

421
00:22:40,640 --> 00:22:41,920
[SPEAKER_00] u svoju novu zajednicu.

422
00:22:41,920 --> 00:22:44,940
[SPEAKER_00] I čak i ide dalje.

423
00:22:44,940 --> 00:22:48,420
[SPEAKER_00] Čak i neke plemenite norme

424
00:22:48,420 --> 00:22:49,579
[SPEAKER_00] koji danas žive kod nas

425
00:22:49,579 --> 00:22:50,559
[SPEAKER_00] ovdje u ovom narodu.

426
00:22:50,559 --> 00:22:52,900
[SPEAKER_00] Obitelj je tad bila sveta.

427
00:22:52,900 --> 00:22:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] Najviša društvena

428
00:22:56,000 --> 00:22:57,200
[SPEAKER_00] i kulturna točka društva.

429
00:22:57,200 --> 00:22:57,740
[SPEAKER_00] Obitelj.

430
00:22:57,740 --> 00:23:00,420
[SPEAKER_00] Nažalost ovdje kod nas

431
00:23:00,420 --> 00:23:01,299
[SPEAKER_00] nije tako jako

432
00:23:01,299 --> 00:23:02,660
[SPEAKER_00] ali i dalje se to osjeća.

433
00:23:02,660 --> 00:23:05,619
[SPEAKER_00] Isus stavlja ispred te obitelji

434
00:23:05,619 --> 00:23:08,400
[SPEAKER_00] sabiranje plemena.

435
00:23:08,400 --> 00:23:09,200
[SPEAKER_00] Ovu novu obitelj

436
00:23:09,200 --> 00:23:10,319
[SPEAKER_00] koju treba skupiti.

437
00:23:10,319 --> 00:23:12,519
[SPEAKER_00] On kaže

438
00:23:12,519 --> 00:23:15,200
[SPEAKER_00] kad ga je pitao jedan učenik

439
00:23:15,200 --> 00:23:16,539
[SPEAKER_00] ja bi te slijedio

440
00:23:16,539 --> 00:23:18,119
[SPEAKER_00] ali mogu prvo ić pokopat svog oca.

441
00:23:18,119 --> 00:23:19,279
[SPEAKER_00] Pa komi to ne bi dao

442
00:23:19,279 --> 00:23:20,140
[SPEAKER_00] sad da neko umre

443
00:23:20,140 --> 00:23:21,759
[SPEAKER_00] i sad da nećeš pokopat svog oca.

444
00:23:23,099 --> 00:23:25,500
[SPEAKER_00] A Isus pomalo grubo kaže

445
00:23:25,500 --> 00:23:28,119
[SPEAKER_00] neka mrtvi pokapaju svoje mrtve.

446
00:23:28,119 --> 00:23:32,480
[SPEAKER_00] Kraljestvo Bože je ispred toga.

447
00:23:32,480 --> 00:23:34,619
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ne zato što Isus je beščutan

448
00:23:34,619 --> 00:23:36,740
[SPEAKER_00] nego zato što daje novi ideal

449
00:23:36,740 --> 00:23:38,259
[SPEAKER_00] novu normu koja je veća

450
00:23:38,259 --> 00:23:40,279
[SPEAKER_00] novu ljubav koju treba iskazati

451
00:23:40,279 --> 00:23:41,259
[SPEAKER_00] veću od one ljubavi

452
00:23:41,259 --> 00:23:43,440
[SPEAKER_00] nego da pokopaš svog oca.

453
00:23:45,359 --> 00:23:46,920
[SPEAKER_00] Poziva da sabereš plemena

454
00:23:46,920 --> 00:23:47,880
[SPEAKER_00] sve odbačene

455
00:23:47,880 --> 00:23:49,700
[SPEAKER_00] sve oni koji traže Boga

456
00:23:49,700 --> 00:23:51,200
[SPEAKER_00] koji ga čekaju.

457
00:23:51,200 --> 00:23:56,700
[SPEAKER_00] I tu se mi moramo pitat.

458
00:23:57,519 --> 00:24:00,299
[SPEAKER_00] I danas se sabiru plemena.

459
00:24:00,299 --> 00:24:03,460
[SPEAKER_00] Isus je uzeo 12 apostola.

460
00:24:03,460 --> 00:24:04,299
[SPEAKER_00] Simbolično.

461
00:24:04,299 --> 00:24:06,539
[SPEAKER_00] I dajemo onu ideju

462
00:24:06,539 --> 00:24:07,859
[SPEAKER_00] koja je trebala biti od početka.

463
00:24:07,859 --> 00:24:09,819
[SPEAKER_00] Da to budu predstavnici plemena

464
00:24:09,819 --> 00:24:12,140
[SPEAKER_00] koji će zajednički moliti

465
00:24:12,140 --> 00:24:13,559
[SPEAKER_00] i imati zajednički cilj.

466
00:24:13,559 --> 00:24:15,940
[SPEAKER_00] I onda ih šalje.

467
00:24:15,940 --> 00:24:17,960
[SPEAKER_00] Navješćujte, izgonite zloduhe.

468
00:24:17,960 --> 00:24:21,380
[SPEAKER_00] Recite, došlo je kraljevstvo Božje.

469
00:24:21,380 --> 00:24:23,420
[SPEAKER_00] Ozdravljajte bolesne.

470
00:24:26,259 --> 00:24:27,940
[SPEAKER_00] I onda je poslije poslao još

471
00:24:27,940 --> 00:24:29,380
[SPEAKER_00] sedamdeset dvojicu.

472
00:24:29,380 --> 00:24:31,119
[SPEAKER_00] Još šest puta dvanest.

473
00:24:31,119 --> 00:24:33,019
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, sve puta dvanest sve ukupno.

474
00:24:33,019 --> 00:24:35,440
[SPEAKER_00] I to je bila prva jezgra

475
00:24:35,440 --> 00:24:36,460
[SPEAKER_00] novog Izraela

476
00:24:36,460 --> 00:24:40,180
[SPEAKER_00] iz kojoj će nastati crkva

477
00:24:40,180 --> 00:24:44,299
[SPEAKER_00] koja se sabire

478
00:24:44,299 --> 00:24:46,180
[SPEAKER_00] sa sve četiri strane svijeta.

479
00:24:46,180 --> 00:24:49,480
[SPEAKER_00] Isus je to učinio.

480
00:24:49,480 --> 00:24:51,359
[SPEAKER_00] Sabro je plemena.

481
00:24:51,359 --> 00:24:53,240
[SPEAKER_00] Drugu stvar koju je trebao napraviti

482
00:24:53,240 --> 00:24:55,359
[SPEAKER_00] je očistiti Jeruzalamski hram.

483
00:24:56,259 --> 00:24:59,680
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, volio bi vam prije

484
00:24:59,680 --> 00:25:00,680
[SPEAKER_00] nego što vam objasnim

485
00:25:00,680 --> 00:25:02,059
[SPEAKER_00] kako je on očistio hram

486
00:25:02,059 --> 00:25:04,559
[SPEAKER_00] malo pojasniti misteri hrama.

487
00:25:04,559 --> 00:25:05,940
[SPEAKER_00] On ide još od Edema

488
00:25:05,940 --> 00:25:08,059
[SPEAKER_00] Edena od Adama.

489
00:25:10,579 --> 00:25:13,440
[SPEAKER_00] Adam je bio čovjek koji je hodio s Bogom.

490
00:25:14,000 --> 00:25:15,940
[SPEAKER_00] I u svakom trenutku

491
00:25:15,940 --> 00:25:17,420
[SPEAKER_00] neometano je mogao ući

492
00:25:17,420 --> 00:25:18,579
[SPEAKER_00] u adoraciju.

493
00:25:18,579 --> 00:25:21,160
[SPEAKER_00] Adoracija je dolazi od riječi

494
00:25:21,160 --> 00:25:21,799
[SPEAKER_00] adoratio

495
00:25:21,799 --> 00:25:23,579
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno od ad ora

496
00:25:23,579 --> 00:25:25,160
[SPEAKER_00] što znači na usta.

497
00:25:25,160 --> 00:25:27,380
[SPEAKER_00] Bio je usta na usta.

498
00:25:27,380 --> 00:25:28,839
[SPEAKER_00] S nekim toliko blizak.

499
00:25:28,839 --> 00:25:30,420
[SPEAKER_00] Iz tog odnosa s gospodinom

500
00:25:30,420 --> 00:25:31,599
[SPEAKER_00] koji je imao

501
00:25:31,599 --> 00:25:34,420
[SPEAKER_00] život mu je bio harmoničan.

502
00:25:34,420 --> 00:25:36,400
[SPEAKER_00] Sve mu se složilo.

503
00:25:37,660 --> 00:25:39,619
[SPEAKER_00] U harmoni su bili osjećaj, misli,

504
00:25:39,619 --> 00:25:40,779
[SPEAKER_00] duh, duša, tijelo,

505
00:25:40,779 --> 00:25:41,960
[SPEAKER_00] seksualnost.

506
00:25:41,960 --> 00:25:43,859
[SPEAKER_00] Sve je bilo posloženo.

507
00:25:43,859 --> 00:25:45,319
[SPEAKER_00] Raj je bio.

508
00:25:45,319 --> 00:25:48,240
[SPEAKER_00] A uzrok tome je bio taj odnos.

509
00:25:48,240 --> 00:25:49,880
[SPEAKER_00] Adoraciju.

510
00:25:49,880 --> 00:25:53,440
[SPEAKER_00] Izraelski narod je imao

511
00:25:53,440 --> 00:25:54,880
[SPEAKER_00] u hramu

512
00:25:54,880 --> 00:25:57,059
[SPEAKER_00] istu svečaničku dužnost.

513
00:25:57,059 --> 00:25:59,880
[SPEAKER_00] Klanjati se Bogu.

514
00:25:59,880 --> 00:26:00,960
[SPEAKER_00] Adorirati.

515
00:26:00,960 --> 00:26:04,720
[SPEAKER_00] Da bi njihova dijela tad

516
00:26:04,720 --> 00:26:07,019
[SPEAKER_00] se očitovala svijetu.

517
00:26:07,480 --> 00:26:08,759
[SPEAKER_00] da bi bila u harmoniji.

518
00:26:08,759 --> 00:26:10,299
[SPEAKER_00] Da bi bili posloženi.

519
00:26:10,299 --> 00:26:14,099
[SPEAKER_00] Oni su trebali biti magnet.

520
00:26:14,099 --> 00:26:17,099
[SPEAKER_00] I teologija, i židovska,

521
00:26:17,099 --> 00:26:18,180
[SPEAKER_00] i naša, kršćanska,

522
00:26:18,180 --> 00:26:19,839
[SPEAKER_00] upravo o tome govori.

523
00:26:19,839 --> 00:26:20,680
[SPEAKER_00] I naša osobna.

524
00:26:20,680 --> 00:26:22,380
[SPEAKER_00] Možemo prenijeti na osobnu razinu.

525
00:26:22,380 --> 00:26:25,579
[SPEAKER_00] Ono što se događa iznutra

526
00:26:25,579 --> 00:26:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] je bitnije od onog izvana.

527
00:26:27,000 --> 00:26:30,680
[SPEAKER_00] Jer ako iznutra častiš Boga,

528
00:26:30,680 --> 00:26:32,460
[SPEAKER_00] na van dolazi red.

529
00:26:32,460 --> 00:26:34,940
[SPEAKER_00] A često se zna dogodi

530
00:26:34,940 --> 00:26:36,579
[SPEAKER_00] da mi slažemo red izvana,

531
00:26:37,079 --> 00:26:38,359
[SPEAKER_00] a iznutra je totalni nered

532
00:26:38,359 --> 00:26:39,180
[SPEAKER_00] i to ne obstaje.

533
00:26:39,180 --> 00:26:42,680
[SPEAKER_00] I Pao je danas pisao o tome.

534
00:26:42,680 --> 00:26:44,859
[SPEAKER_00] Često želimo živjeti po zakonu,

535
00:26:44,859 --> 00:26:45,980
[SPEAKER_00] ali zakon nas osuđuje.

536
00:26:45,980 --> 00:26:48,559
[SPEAKER_00] Treba živjeti po vjeri.

537
00:26:49,539 --> 00:26:50,900
[SPEAKER_00] I oni su znali da iz ispravnog

538
00:26:50,900 --> 00:26:53,079
[SPEAKER_00] pravovjernog bogoštovlja,

539
00:26:53,079 --> 00:26:54,460
[SPEAKER_00] prema jedinom pravom Bogu,

540
00:26:54,460 --> 00:26:55,140
[SPEAKER_00] dolazi red.

541
00:26:55,779 --> 00:26:57,220
[SPEAKER_00] Isto tako i danas.

542
00:26:57,220 --> 00:27:01,019
[SPEAKER_00] I to su radili u hramu.

543
00:27:01,019 --> 00:27:02,839
[SPEAKER_00] Koji je bio pun simbolike

544
00:27:02,839 --> 00:27:04,700
[SPEAKER_00] Edena, zvijezde,

545
00:27:04,700 --> 00:27:06,460
[SPEAKER_00] mjesec, voda, vatra,

546
00:27:06,460 --> 00:27:09,059
[SPEAKER_00] zemlja.

547
00:27:11,119 --> 00:27:12,440
[SPEAKER_00] I hram je uz to bio

548
00:27:12,440 --> 00:27:14,299
[SPEAKER_00] centar Izraela.

549
00:27:14,299 --> 00:27:16,019
[SPEAKER_00] Sve što se moglo događati

550
00:27:16,019 --> 00:27:16,980
[SPEAKER_00] na društvenoj razini,

551
00:27:16,980 --> 00:27:18,839
[SPEAKER_00] na političkoj,

552
00:27:18,839 --> 00:27:19,619
[SPEAKER_00] na religioznog,

553
00:27:19,619 --> 00:27:20,759
[SPEAKER_00] događalo se u hramu.

554
00:27:20,759 --> 00:27:22,420
[SPEAKER_00] To je bilo boravište Jahve.

555
00:27:23,700 --> 00:27:25,680
[SPEAKER_00] I ništa nije bilo veće od toga,

556
00:27:25,680 --> 00:27:26,660
[SPEAKER_00] osim Jahve.

557
00:27:26,660 --> 00:27:28,220
[SPEAKER_00] I onda dolazi Isus,

558
00:27:28,220 --> 00:27:31,200
[SPEAKER_00] taj lik,

559
00:27:31,200 --> 00:27:34,339
[SPEAKER_00] tamo već pred kraj svoje službe,

560
00:27:34,339 --> 00:27:35,240
[SPEAKER_00] ulazi u Jeruzalem,

561
00:27:35,240 --> 00:27:36,559
[SPEAKER_00] izazove svađu,

562
00:27:36,559 --> 00:27:37,559
[SPEAKER_00] uzme bić,

563
00:27:37,559 --> 00:27:39,960
[SPEAKER_00] odužeta,

564
00:27:39,960 --> 00:27:42,319
[SPEAKER_00] razbaca stolove mjenjačima,

565
00:27:42,319 --> 00:27:44,339
[SPEAKER_00] kaže dom moj,

566
00:27:44,339 --> 00:27:47,440
[SPEAKER_00] dom moj će se zvati

567
00:27:47,440 --> 00:27:49,880
[SPEAKER_00] dom molitve za svagda.

568
00:27:49,880 --> 00:27:53,460
[SPEAKER_00] A vi od njega načiniste,

569
00:27:53,700 --> 00:27:55,059
[SPEAKER_00] pećinu razbojničku.

570
00:27:55,059 --> 00:27:57,900
[SPEAKER_00] Počeo joj čistiti.

571
00:27:57,900 --> 00:27:59,339
[SPEAKER_00] I onda su ga pitali,

572
00:27:59,339 --> 00:28:00,700
[SPEAKER_00] kako ti to smiješ rajit?

573
00:28:00,700 --> 00:28:02,299
[SPEAKER_00] Znate šta je on odgovorio?

574
00:28:02,299 --> 00:28:03,900
[SPEAKER_00] On je rekao,

575
00:28:03,900 --> 00:28:07,319
[SPEAKER_00] razvalite ovaj hram,

576
00:28:07,319 --> 00:28:10,160
[SPEAKER_00] ja ću ga podići u tri dana.

577
00:28:10,160 --> 00:28:13,259
[SPEAKER_00] Pojo ih je.

578
00:28:13,259 --> 00:28:16,599
[SPEAKER_00] Židovima pikno ih je,

579
00:28:16,599 --> 00:28:17,980
[SPEAKER_00] vjerojatno je zbog toga i umro,

580
00:28:17,980 --> 00:28:20,160
[SPEAKER_00] jer nisu samo židovi bili tamo,

581
00:28:20,160 --> 00:28:21,380
[SPEAKER_00] nego i rimljani,

582
00:28:21,380 --> 00:28:23,059
[SPEAKER_00] koji su pratili šta se događa u Rimu

583
00:28:23,059 --> 00:28:24,319
[SPEAKER_00] i vidili su da su neki nemiri.

584
00:28:24,319 --> 00:28:27,240
[SPEAKER_00] Dirno im je hrama.

585
00:28:27,240 --> 00:28:28,279
[SPEAKER_00] Prije toga Isus,

586
00:28:28,279 --> 00:28:30,940
[SPEAKER_00] također su ga tad htjeli ubiti,

587
00:28:30,940 --> 00:28:31,480
[SPEAKER_00] on kaže,

588
00:28:31,480 --> 00:28:33,079
